                                    .:PLOT:.

                     The staff of Carlo's Bakery in Hoboken, New Jersey, 
                led by Buddy Valastro, shows how it prepares elaborate 
                themed cakes for various occasions. Each episode typically 
                features the preparation of two cakes for events including 
                receptions, charity events and theme parties as well as 
                weddings and birthdays.
    
